ygData.messageBody:
if you mean lullaby, starting off that song isn't too effective. it starts
to be useful around 21+. it's a great taunt tho when you need it. (i went
for weeks wondering what the song did) strings do help A LOT. if you just
got the song, i'm not sure if it'll become effective enough to be reliable.
